wlanpi-fpms2 (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release — decoupled state/display architecture
  * FastAPI state service with WebSocket broadcast (Phase 1)
  * wlanpi-core HMAC client with full action registry (Phase 2)
  * OLED screen thin client with PIL renderer (Phase 3)
  * Textual TUI client (Phase 5)
  * Cockpit web plugin with polling transport (Phase 6)
  * Complications API for third-party status indicators
  * Status bar indicators: battery, temperature, WiFi adapter count
  * Mode-specific home screens (classic, hotspot, server, bridge)
  * Home page QR code toggle (profiler/hotspot WiFi credentials)
  * KEY1/KEY2/KEY3 shortcut navigation
  * Profiler new-device notification popup
  * Boot splash animation and shutdown/reboot display images
  * Eth0 carrier-change screen wake
  * Display orientation persistence and flipped button remapping
  * Debian packaging with dh-virtualenv, Cockpit plugin install,
    and systemd service ordering (After/Wants wlanpi-core)
  * Conflicts with wlanpi-fpms (mutually exclusive)

